CNCP v1 24290
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#3533: 开发环境中删除自定义指令无法触发unmounted事件",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:27:51.500840+00:00",
  "text": "开发环境中删除自定义指令无法触发unmounted事件\n\n### Version\r\n3.0.11\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://github.com/xxxxst/issure-vue-directive](https://github.com/xxxxst/issure-vue-directive)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n代码基于vue webpack typescript，修改&lt;template&gt;里的数据，浏览器会自动更新页面。\r\n\r\n然而，如果删除了一个自定义指令，unmounted()事件无法触发，这意味着无法正确的进行指令清理工作，必须要刷新浏览器才能正确地移除指令。\r\n\r\n重新添加指令后，不会触发mounted()事件，而是触发updated()事件。似乎Vue将指令缓存了起来。\r\n\r\n在vue2中没有这个问题，我不确定这是bug还是设计成这样，这不影响生产环境，但确实会影响开发体验。\r\n\r\n重现步骤\r\n\r\n- 在组件中添加自定义指令\r\n- 移除指令，unmounted事件不触发。刷新浏览器后，指令可以正确的被移除。\r\n- 重新添加指令，仅触发updated事件\r\n\r\nApp.vue\r\n\r\n```\r\n<template>\r\n<div id=\"nav\" v-test>\r\n\t\r\n</div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<style lang=\"scss\">\r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\nmain.ts\r\n```ts\r\nimport { createApp } from 'vue'\r\nimport App from './App.vue'\r\n\r\nconst app = createApp(App);\r\n\r\napp.directive('test', {\r\n\tbeforeMount: function (el, data: any, tag: any) {\r\n\t\tconsole.info(\"beforeMount\");\r\n\t},\r\n\tmounted: function (el, data: any, tag: any) {\r\n\t\tconsole.info(\"mounted\");\r\n\t},\r\n\tbeforeUpdate: function (el, data: any, tag: any) {\r\n\t\tconsole.info(\"beforeUpdate\");\r\n\t},\r\n\tupdated() {\r\n\t\tconsole.info(\"updated\");\r\n\t},\r\n\tbeforeUnmount: function (el, data: any, tag: any) {\r\n\t\tconsole.info(\"beforeUnmount\");\r\n\t},\r\n\tunmounted: function (el, data: any, tag: any) {\r\n\t\tconsole.info(\"unmounted\");\r\n\t}\r\n})\r\n\r\napp.mount('#app')\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n![step](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xxxxst/issure-vue-directive/master/aaa.png)\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n删除指令能够正确触发unmounted事件\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n删除指令无法触发unmounted事件\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
  "language": "en",
